  @property --gb-pos-x { 

    syntax: '<percentage>'; 

    initial-value: 11%; 

    inherits: false; 

  } 

  @property --gb-pos-y { 

    syntax: '<percentage>'; 

    initial-value: 140%; 

    inherits: false; 

  } 

  @property --gb-spread-x { 

    syntax: '<percentage>'; 

    initial-value: 150%; 

    inherits: false; 

  } 

  @property --gb-spread-y { 

    syntax: '<percentage>'; 

    initial-value: 180%; 

    inherits: false; 

  } 

  @property --gb-c1 { syntax: '<color>'; initial-value: #0a0030; inherits: false; } 

  @property --gb-c2 { syntax: '<color>'; initial-value: #1a0060; inherits: false; } 

  @property --gb-c3 { syntax: '<color>'; initial-value: #3B5BFF; inherits: false; }

  @property --gb-stop1 { syntax: '<percentage>'; initial-value: 37%; inherits: false; } 

  @property --gb-stop2 { syntax: '<percentage>'; initial-value: 61%; inherits: false; } 

  @property --gb-stop3 { syntax: '<percentage>'; initial-value: 78%; inherits: false; } 

  @property --gb-stop4 { syntax: '<percentage>'; initial-value: 89%; inherits: false; } 

  @property --gb-stop5 { syntax: '<percentage>'; initial-value: 100%; inherits: false; }

  @property --gb-border-c1 { syntax: '<color>'; initial-value: hsla(220,80%,70%,0.25); inherits: false; } 

  @property --gb-border-c2 { syntax: '<color>'; initial-value: hsla(280,90%,65%,0.8); inherits: false; } 

 

  .gradient-button { 

    position: relative; 

    display: inline-flex; 

    align-items: center;

    border: none;

      var(--gb-c3) var(--gb-stop3), 

      var(--gb-c4) var(--gb-stop4), 

      var(--gb-c5) var(--gb-stop5) 

    );

      --gb-pos-x 0.55s ease, 

      --gb-pos-y 0.55s ease, 

      --gb-spread-x 0.55s ease, 

      --gb-spread-y 0.55s ease, 

      --gb-c1 0.55s ease, 

      --gb-c2 0.55s ease, 

      --gb-c3 0.55s ease, 

      --gb-c4 0.55s ease,

  <!-- SLIDE 4: Como Funciona --> 

  <section class="slide" id="slide-como" data-theme="dark"> 

    <div class="container"> 

      <div class="slide-content"> 

        <div class="label">Como Funciona</div> 

        <h2 class="section-title" style="color:#fff;">Etapas do Processo</h2> 

      </div> 

      <div class="steps-grid stagger"> 

        <div class="step-card glow-card"> 

      <div class="glow-border" style="--glow-border-width:1.5px;--glow-spread:18;--glow-gradient:radial-gradient(circle, #7B5BFF 10%, #7B5BFF00 20%),                 radial-gradient(circle at 40% 40%, #FF3B8F 5%, #FF3B8F00 15%),                 radial-gradient(circle at 60% 60%, #3B5BFF 10%, #3B5BFF00 20%),                  radial-gradient(circle at 40% 60%, #a855f7 10%, #a855f700 20%),                 repeating-conic-gradient(                   from 236.84deg at 50% 50%,                   #7B5BFF 0%,                   #FF3B8F calc(25% / 5),                   #3B5BFF calc(50% / 5),                    #a855f7 calc(75% / 5),                   #7B5BFF calc(100% / 5)                 )"></div> 

          <div class="step-num">1</div> 

          <div class="step-title">Análise de dados</div> 

          <p class="step-text">Conectamos às suas fontes de dados existentes — ERP, sistemas de ponto de venda (POS), sistemas de armazém — e construímos um conjunto de dados limpo e rico em atributos.<br><br>Nosso modelo trata automaticamente valores ausentes, outliers e o alinhamento temporal dos dados. <span class="accent">Sem alterar nada no banco de dados.</span></p> 

        </div> 

        <div class="step-card glow-card"> 

      <div class="glow-border" style="--glow-border-width:1.5px;--glow-spread:18;--glow-gradient:radial-gradient(circle, #7B5BFF 10%, #7B5BFF00 20%),                 radial-gradient(circle at 40% 40%, #FF3B8F 5%, #FF3B8F00 15%),                 radial-gradient(circle at 60% 60%, #3B5BFF 10%, #3B5BFF00 20%),                  radial-gradient(circle at 40% 60%, #a855f7 10%, #a855f700 20%),                 repeating-conic-gradient(                   from 236.84deg at 50% 50%,                   #7B5BFF 0%,                   #FF3B8F calc(25% / 5),                   #3B5BFF calc(50% / 5),                    #a855f7 calc(75% / 5),                   #7B5BFF calc(100% / 5)                 )"></div> 

          <div class="step-num">2</div> 

          <div class="step-title">Aplicação do Machine Learning</div> 

          <p class="step-text">Utilizando técnicas avançadas como Regressão Quantílica e Gradient Boosting, <span class="accent">treinamos modelos capazes de capturar padrões complexos de demanda.</span><br><br>A validação cruzada garante previsões robustas e confiáveis.</p> 

        </div> 

        <div class="step-card glow-card"> 

      <div class="glow-border" style="--glow-border-width:1.5px;--glow-spread:18;--glow-gradient:radial-gradient(circle, #7B5BFF 10%, #7B5BFF00 20%),                 radial-gradient(circle at 40% 40%, #FF3B8F 5%, #FF3B8F00 15%),                 radial-gradient(circle at 60% 60%, #3B5BFF 10%, #3B5BFF00 20%),                  radial-gradient(circle at 40% 60%, #a855f7 10%, #a855f700 20%),                 repeating-conic-gradient(                   from 236.84deg at 50% 50%,                   #7B5BFF 0%,                   #FF3B8F calc(25% / 5),                   #3B5BFF calc(50% / 5),                    #a855f7 calc(75% / 5),                   #7B5BFF calc(100% / 5)                 )"></div> 

          <div class="step-num">3</div> 

          <div class="step-title">Implementação</div> 

          <p class="step-text">As previsões se transformam em recomendações acionáveis. Implementamos dashboards interativos com análise de cenários, <span class="accent">permitindo que sua equipe ajuste estratégias e visualize o impacto em tempo real.</span></p> 

        </div> 

      </div> 

    </div> 

  </section> 

 

  <!-- SLIDE 5: Estudo de Caso --> 

  <section class="slide" id="slide-case" data-theme="dark"> 

    <div class="container"> 

      <div class="slide-content"> 

        <div class="label">Estudo de Caso</div> 

        <h2 class="section-title" style="color:#fff;"> 

          Resultados obtidos no setor de <span class="grad-text">Moda Feminina</span> 

        </h2> 

        <div class="case-intro"> 

          <p>Uma grande varejista de moda enfrentava um dilema crítico: <span class="accent-pink">excesso recorrente de estoque em algumas regiões e rupturas em outras</span>. A empresa recorreu à Shift para transformar seu planejamento de estoque.</p> 

        </div> 

      </div> 

      <div class="case-grid stagger"> 

        <div class="case-card desafio glow-card"> 

      <div class="glow-border" style="--glow-border-width:2px;--glow-spread:18;--glow-gradient:radial-gradient(circle, #7B5BFF 10%, #7B5BFF00 20%),                 radial-gradient(circle at 40% 40%, #FF3B8F 5%, #FF3B8F00 15%),                 radial-gradient(circle at 60% 60%, #3B5BFF 10%, #3B5BFF00 20%),                  radial-gradient(circle at 40% 60%, #a855f7 10%, #a855f700 20%),                 repeating-conic-gradient(                   from 236.84deg at 50% 50%,                   #7B5BFF 0%,                   #FF3B8F calc(25% / 5),                   #3B5BFF calc(50% / 5),                    #a855f7 calc(75% / 5),                   #7B5BFF calc(100% / 5)                 )"></div> 

          <h3>Desafio</h3> 

          <ul> 

            <li>Milhões em capital de giro imobilizados em estoques de baixa rotatividade.</li> 

            <li>O planejamento manual demorava meses para conseguir montar a nova coleção.</li> 

            <li>Reposição muito acima da demanda real em diversas lojas.</li> 

          </ul> 

        </div> 

        <div class="case-card solucao glow-card"> 

      <div class="glow-border" style="--glow-border-width:2px;--glow-spread:18;--glow-gradient:radial-gradient(circle, #7B5BFF 10%, #7B5BFF00 20%),                 radial-gradient(circle at 40% 40%, #FF3B8F 5%, #FF3B8F00 15%),                 radial-gradient(circle at 60% 60%, #3B5BFF 10%, #3B5BFF00 20%),                  radial-gradient(circle at 40% 60%, #a855f7 10%, #a855f700 20%),                 repeating-conic-gradient(                   from 236.84deg at 50% 50%,                   #7B5BFF 0%,                   #FF3B8F calc(25% / 5),                   #3B5BFF calc(50% / 5),                    #a855f7 calc(75% / 5),                   #7B5BFF calc(100% / 5)                 )"></div> 

          <h3>Solução</h3> 

          <ul> 

            <li>Implementamos previsão probabilística para quantificar a incerteza da demanda.</li> 

            <li>Otimizamos os níveis de estoque por filial com base em metas de nível de serviço.</li> 

            <li>Implantamos dashboards em tempo real para monitoramento contínuo.</li> 

          </ul> 

        </div> 

      </div> 

    </div> 

  </section>

<script data-cfasync="false" src="/cdn-cgi/scripts/5c5dd728/cloudflare-static/email-decode.min.js"></script><script> 

  const slider = document.getElementById('slider'); 

  const slides = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.slide')); 

  const dots   = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.dot')); 

  const nav    = document.getElementById('main-nav'); 

  let current  = 0; 

  let isScrolling = false; 

 

  // ── Go to slide ── 

  function goTo(index) { 

    if (index < 0 || index >= slides.length) return; 

    current = index; 

    slides[index].scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' }); 

  } 

 

  // ── Keyboard nav ── 

  document.addEventListener('keydown', e => { 

    if (e.key === 'ArrowDown' || e.key === 'PageDown') goTo(current + 1); 

    if (e.key === 'ArrowUp'   || e.key === 'PageUp'  ) goTo(current - 1); 

  }); 

 

  // ── Intersection Observer: detect active slide ── 

  const io = new IntersectionObserver(entries => { 

    entries.forEach(entry => { 

      if (!entry.isIntersecting) return; 

      const idx = slides.indexOf(entry.target); 

      if (idx === -1) return; 

      current = idx; 

 

      // dots 

      dots.forEach((d, i) => { 

        d.classList.toggle('active', i === idx); 

      }); 

 

      // nav theme 

      const theme = entry.target.dataset.theme; 

      nav.classList.toggle('dark-nav', theme === 'dark'); 

 

      // dots color 

      const dotsEl = document.getElementById('dots'); 

      dots.forEach(d => d.classList.toggle('dark', theme === 'dark')); 

 

      // animate slide content 

      entry.target.classList.add('in-view'); 

 

      // counter animation for impacto slide 

      if (entry.target.id === 'slide-impacto') { 

        entry.target.querySelectorAll('.count-up').forEach(el => { 

          if (el.dataset.done) return; 

          el.dataset.done = '1'; 

          const target = parseInt(el.dataset.target); 

          let val = 0; 

          const step = target / 55; 

          const t = setInterval(() => { 

            val += step; 

            if (val >= target) { val = target; clearInterval(t); } 

            el.textContent = Math.floor(val); 

          }, 18); 

        }); 

      } 

    }); 

  }, { threshold: 0.55 }); 

 

  slides.forEach(s => io.observe(s)); 

 

  // ── Touch / trackpad: smoother wheel handling ── 

  let wheelTimer = null; 

  slider.addEventListener('wheel', e => { 

    // let CSS scroll-snap handle it naturally, just block rapid re-trigger 

    clearTimeout(wheelTimer); 

    wheelTimer = setTimeout(() => {}, 800); 

  }, { passive: true }); 

 

  // Trigger first slide 

  slides[0].classList.add('in-view'); 

</script> 

 

<script> 

(function() { 

  const PROXIMITY = 40;        // menor área de ativação 

  const INACTIVE_ZONE = 0.4;   // zona morta maior no centro 

  const SMOOTH = 0.06;         // interpolação por frame — menor = mais lento/suave 

 

  const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.glow-card'); 

  const cardStates = new Map(); 

  cards.forEach(card => { 

    cardStates.set(card, { angle: 0, targetAngle: 0, active: 0, targetActive: 0 }); 

  }); 

 

  function angleDiff(from, to) { 

    return ((to - from + 180) % 360) - 180; 

  } 

 

  let lastX = 0, lastY = 0; 

 

  function tick() { 

    cards.forEach(card => { 

      const state = cardStates.get(card); 

      const rect = card.getBoundingClientRect(); 

      const cx = rect.left + rect.width * 0.5; 

      const cy = rect.top + rect.height * 0.5; 

 

      const dist = Math.hypot(lastX - cx, lastY - cy); 

      const inactiveR = 0.5 * Math.min(rect.width, rect.height) * INACTIVE_ZONE; 

 

      const inside = 

        lastX > rect.left - PROXIMITY && 

        lastX < rect.left + rect.width + PROXIMITY && 

        lastY > rect.top - PROXIMITY && 

        lastY < rect.top + rect.height + PROXIMITY; 

 

      const shouldBeActive = inside && dist > inactiveR ? 1 : 0; 

 

      // Lerp opacity 

      state.active += (shouldBeActive - state.active) * 0.08; 

      card.style.setProperty('--glow-active', state.active.toFixed(3)); 

 

      if (shouldBeActive) { 

        let raw = (180 * Math.atan2(lastY - cy, lastX - cx)) / Math.PI + 90; 

        const diff = angleDiff(state.angle, raw); 

        state.targetAngle = state.angle + diff; 

      } 

 

      // Lerp angle — very smooth follow 

      state.angle += (state.targetAngle - state.angle) * SMOOTH; 

      card.style.setProperty('--glow-start', state.angle.toFixed(2)); 

    }); 

 

    requestAnimationFrame(tick); 

  } 

 

  requestAnimationFrame(tick); 

 

  window.addEventListener('pointermove', e => { 

    lastX = e.clientX; 

    lastY = e.clientY; 

  }, { passive: true }); 

 

  document.getElementById('slider').addEventListener('scroll', () => {}, { passive: true }); 

})(); 

</script> 

 

 

<script> 

// Privacy Policy Modal 

function openPrivacy() { 

  const overlay = document.getElementById('privacy-overlay'); 

  overlay.style.display = 'flex'; 

  // reset scroll e progress 

  const body = document.getElementById('privacy-body'); 

  body.scrollTop = 0; 

  document.getElementById('privacy-progress-bar').style.width = '0%'; 

  const accept = document.getElementById('privacy-accept'); 

  accept.disabled = true; 

  accept.style.opacity = '0.45'; 

  accept.style.cursor = 'not-allowed'; 

  // trap focus 

  document.getElementById('privacy-close').focus(); 

} 

 

function closePrivacy() { 

  document.getElementById('privacy-overlay').style.display = 'none'; 

} 

 

function acceptPrivacy() { 

  closePrivacy(); 

} 

 

function privacyScroll() { 

  const body = document.getElementById('privacy-body'); 

  const progress = Math.min(1, body.scrollTop / (body.scrollHeight - body.clientHeight)); 

  document.getElementById('privacy-progress-bar').style.width = (progress * 100) + '%'; 

 

  const accept = document.getElementById('privacy-accept'); 

  if (progress >= 0.98) { 

    accept.disabled = false; 

    accept.style.opacity = '1'; 

    accept.style.cursor = 'pointer'; 

  } 

} 

 

// Close on backdrop click 

document.getElementById('privacy-backdrop').addEventListener('click', closePrivacy); 

 

// Close on Escape 

document.addEventListener('keydown', e => { 

  if (e.key === 'Escape') closePrivacy(); 

}); 

</script> 

 

 

<script> 

// StarButton — luz viajando pelo perímetro do botão 

(function() { 

  function initStarButtons() { 

    document.querySelectorAll('.star-button').forEach(btn => { 

      if (btn._starInited) return; 

      btn._starInited = true; 

 

      const light = btn.querySelector('.star-btn-light'); 

      if (!light) return; 

 

      const duration = parseFloat(btn.dataset.duration || '3') * 1000; 

      let start = null; 

      let raf = null; 

 

      function getPerimeter(w, h, r) { 

        // approximate perimeter of rounded rect with radius r 

        return 2 * (w - 2*r) + 2 * (h - 2*r) + 2 * Math.PI * r; 

      } 

 

      function pointOnRoundedRect(t, w, h, r) { 

        // t in [0,1] — travel clockwise from top-left corner 

        const perim = getPerimeter(w, h, r); 

        let d = t * perim; 

 

        // Segments: top, top-right corner, right, bottom-right corner, bottom, bottom-left corner, left, top-left corner 

        const top = w - 2*r; 

        const right = h - 2*r; 

        const bottom = w - 2*r; 

        const left = h - 2*r; 

        const cornerLen = (Math.PI / 2) * r; 

 

        let x, y; 

 

        if (d < top) { 

          x = r + d; y = 0; 

        } else if (d < top + cornerLen) { 

          const a = (d - top) / r; 

          x = w - r + Math.sin(a) * r; y = r - Math.cos(a) * r; 

        } else if (d < top + cornerLen + right) { 

          d -= top + cornerLen; 

          x = w; y = r + d; 

        } else if (d < top + cornerLen + right + cornerLen) { 

          d -= top + cornerLen + right; 

          const a = d / r; 

          x = w - r + Math.cos(a) * r; y = h - r + Math.sin(a) * r; 

        } else if (d < top + cornerLen + right + cornerLen + bottom) { 

          d -= top + cornerLen + right + cornerLen; 

          x = w - r - d; y = h; 

        } else if (d < top + cornerLen + right + cornerLen + bottom + cornerLen) { 

          d -= top + cornerLen + right + cornerLen + bottom; 

          const a = d / r; 

          x = r - Math.sin(a) * r; y = h - r + Math.cos(a) * r; 

        } else if (d < top + cornerLen + right + cornerLen + bottom + cornerLen + left) { 

          d -= top + cornerLen + right + cornerLen + bottom + cornerLen; 

          x = 0; y = h - r - d; 

        } else { 

          d -= top + cornerLen + right + cornerLen + bottom + cornerLen + left; 

          const a = d / r; 

          x = r - Math.cos(a) * r; y = r - Math.sin(a) * r; 

        } 

        return { x, y }; 

      } 

 

      function animate(ts) { 

        if (!start) start = ts; 

        const elapsed = (ts - start) % duration; 

        const t = elapsed / duration; 

 

        const w = btn.offsetWidth; 

        const h = btn.offsetHeight; 

        const r = h / 2; // border-radius 50px → ~half height 

 

        const pos = pointOnRoundedRect(t, w, h, r); 

        // Normal vector apontando para fora do botão no ponto atual 

        const nx = pos.x - w / 2; 

        const ny = pos.y - h / 2; 

        const nLen = Math.sqrt(nx*nx + ny*ny) || 1; 

        // Deslocar a luz para fora: centro da luz fica na borda, não dentro 

        const offset = light.offsetWidth * 0.28; // empurra ~28% do raio para fora 

        const cx2 = pos.x + (nx/nLen) * offset - light.offsetWidth / 2; 

        const cy2 = pos.y + (ny/nLen) * offset - light.offsetHeight / 2; 

        light.style.transform = `translate(${cx2}px, ${cy2}px)`; 

        raf = requestAnimationFrame(animate); 

      } 

 

      // Only animate when slide is visible 

      const slide = btn.closest('.slide'); 

      if (slide) { 

        const obs = new IntersectionObserver(entries => { 

          entries.forEach(e => { 

            if (e.isIntersecting) { 

              start = null; 

              raf = requestAnimationFrame(animate); 

            } else { 

              if (raf) cancelAnimationFrame(raf); 

            } 

          }); 

        }, { threshold: 0.3 }); 

        obs.observe(slide); 

      } else { 

        requestAnimationFrame(animate); 

      } 

    }); 

  } 

 

  // Init after DOM ready 

  if (document.readyState === 'loading') { 

    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initStarButtons); 

  } else { 

    initStarButtons(); 

  } 

})(); 

</script> 

 

 

<script> 

// Chroma key — remove fundo verde do vídeo e renderiza no canvas 

(function() { 

  const video  = document.getElementById('logo-video'); 

  const canvas = document.getElementById('logo-canvas'); 

  if (!video || !canvas) return; 

 

  const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d', { willReadFrequently: true }); 

 

  function setup() { 

    canvas.width  = video.videoWidth; 

    canvas.height = video.videoHeight; 

  } 

 

  function chromaFrame() { 

    if (video.readyState < 2) { requestAnimationFrame(chromaFrame); return; } 

 

    ctx.drawImage(video, 0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height); 

    const frame = ctx.getImageData(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height); 

    const d = frame.data; 

 

    for (let i = 0; i < d.length; i += 4) { 

      const r = d[i], g = d[i+1], b = d[i+2]; 

 

      // Detectar verde: G é dominante, R e B são baixos 

      const isGreen = g > 80 

        && g > r * 1.4 

        && g > b * 1.2 

        && r < 160 

        && b < 160; 

 

      if (isGreen) { 

        // Calcular "quão verde" é o pixel para anti-aliasing suave 

        const greenness = Math.min(1, (g - Math.max(r, b)) / 80); 

        d[i+3] = Math.round(d[i+3] * (1 - greenness)); // reduzir alpha 

      } 

    } 

 

    ctx.putImageData(frame, 0, 0); 

    requestAnimationFrame(chromaFrame); 

  } 

 

  video.addEventListener('loadedmetadata', setup); 

  video.addEventListener('play', () => { 

    setup(); 

    requ
